159 amended to read:
16 2-F. Heads of households; tax years beginning 2017 from 2017 to 2029. For tax
17 years beginning on or after January 1, 2017 but not later than December 31, 2029, for
18 unmarried individuals or legally separated individuals who qualify as heads of households:
19 If Maine taxable income is: The tax is:
20 Less than $31,550 5.8% of the Maine taxable income
21 At least $31,550 but less than $75,000 $1,830 plus 6.75% of the excess over
22 $31,550
23 $75,000 or more $4,763 plus 7.15% of the excess over
24 $75,000
